     F******************************************************
     FARMX    IP  F     600            DISK
     FABAWMXF O   E                    DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     E                    MN1    12  12  3
     E                    MN2    12  12  3
      *
     E                    AY        600  1
     E                    DTS        20  8 0
     E                    DTE        20  8 0
     E                    MMS        20  2 0
     E                    DDS        20  2 0
     E                    A21         2  1
      *
     E                    APT        15  1
     E                    AQT         9  1
     E                    SQT         9  1
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     IARMX    AA  01
     I                                        1  12 DAT1
     I                                       13 600 DAT2
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 #PART
     I                                        1   5 AWMHN1
     I                                        6  10 AWMHN2
     I                                       11  15 AWMHN3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 W@MNDD
     I                                        1   3 W@MN
     I                                        4   4 W@DASH
     I                                        5   6 W@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80YMD
     I                                        1   40YEAR
     I                                        5   60MONTH
     I                                        7   80DAY
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80AWENDD
     I                                        1   40F8KAYY
     I                                        5   60F8KAMM
     I                                        7   80F8KADD
